Package: avior
Title: Validation Evidence Compiler for R Package Environments
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Thynexa", "Team", email = "opensource@thynexa.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A local-first evidence compiler for R package validation in
    regulated environments (FDA / EMA / NMPA submissions). Takes a project's
    dependency manifest ('renv.lock') and validation policy as input and
    produces a structured, tamper-evident, signature-ready validation
    evidence bundle: dependency identification, risk scoring via pluggable
    assessment engines, decision records, targeted testing, environment
    fingerprinting, and audit-ready reporting. See the product requirements
    document in the repository for the full file contracts.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/Thynexa/AVIOR
BugReports: https://github.com/Thynexa/AVIOR/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    cli,
    digest,
    jsonlite,
    utils,
    yaml
Suggests:
    riskmetric,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/testthat/edition: 3
